        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-403",
        "content": "They used to make their lemonade out of the juice of wild oranges, sweetened with honey which they got from the bees' nests in hollow trees.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
