        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-403",
        "content": "So all this time, while the Doctor and his animals were going along towards the Land of the Monkeys, thinking themselves quite safe, they were still being followed by the King's men.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
